I can help make it happen! It's open to anyone of you lovely people anywhere in the world and it's not just one top prize we can all win the £1500 or whatever we go for if we want to. I see a group trip coming on and lots of fun! 
The qualification period starts today, you might only need 2 weeks but they are giving us 3 months. Work with me in some of your spare time to win either of these or many more prizes like MacBook Airs, spa experiences, trips to Spain, high spec TV, a personal shopping experience with spends at Selfridges.....the list goes on. Three different levels to qualify and choices of prizes at each level! So exciting. I'm going to get the £1500, that's what I'm after. Which would you like? 
Get in touch, comment or pm me for more info and let's do this together.
